item.title: Shift my Shit with Anikiko
item.description: 21:51 Friday 24 August 2018 JST I took the course tonight with my ex-crush new-coach Anikiko. She created the course 7 (seven) days ago and it started tonight. It will run for 3 weeks and I actually think I will invite some people to join. If you have a budding project ready to jump out of you, I judge this program will get you moving. It has already gotten me moving through just the first hour.

item.title: didnt do shit
item.description: 11:34 Sunday 24 January 2016 PST We were scheduled to be at the wedding location at 10am to help set up centerpieces. I was up and ostensibly ready-within-5-minutes as Fred repeatedly snoozed his alarm around 9 am. He was like, “they won’t be ready by 10am; arriving anytime between 10 and 11 is fine.” We arrived around 11:15. All the centerpieces were done so we left. Had I realllly cared to be there on time, I could have found another driver.
